Syntax: prowl

Toggles prowl mode. Requires the Prowl skill.

While prowling, every time you move the game rolls your Prowl skill
percentage. On a success, others in the room do not see your departure
or arrival. On a failure, you are seen moving normally, but prowl mode
stays active for your next move.

Prowl mode ends when you attack, speak, shout, or type prowl again.

The sneak and hide commands start the same silent-movement mode.

See also: sneak, hide, assassination
